alerts.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued November 14 at 2:43PM CST until November 15 at 9:00AM CST by NWS Kansas City
alerts.description:
...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY NOW IN EFFECT FROM 8 PM THIS EVENING
TO 9 AM CST TUESDAY...
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of up to two
inches.
* WHERE...Portions of east central and northeast Kansas and
north central, northwest and west central Missouri.
* WHEN...From 8 PM this evening to 9 AM CST Tuesday.
* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. The hazardous
conditions could impact the morning commute.
